                            Label: "battle_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Not this spin",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "A Champion at my table. I like long odds. Beat Fritz already, did you? Then you know how this floor pays - fast and all at once. The house always spins."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I have played this Arcade since Company money kept the lights on. Now no coin owns the floor, and the game is finally honest. Care to wager a battle?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Glass cannons and coin flips - that is my whole box. One good roll wins it, one bad one ends it. Same as you spinning your way through the whole region, no?"
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Player Suki",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
